summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Fifty-third Street from Eleventh Avenue N.W. to Fifteenth Avenue N.W. in the City of Seattle, by constructing a sewer under Ordinance No. 17340, creating Local Improvement District No. 1631 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
